                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8422" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0246</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1576 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色筑未来—北新建材的ESG之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green Builds the Future--The ESG Practice of Beixin</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杜军，张帆，于帆，许浩男，寇雅凯</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北新集团建材股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG；绿色债券；价值增值；新质生产力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG; Green bonds; value increment; new quality productivity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“3060”的提出，表明我国高度重视低碳发展，而建筑建材产业链耗能、碳排放均占全社会总体一半以上，建筑建材产业降碳对于落实“双碳”战略具有重要意义。与此同时，后疫情时代下居民更加关注健康，但串串房、高污染建材致病等问题严重损害健康，建材企业产品是否绿色、环保备受关注。北新建材作为我国最大的新型建材产业集团，其ESG实践在推动建材行业减碳、回应消费者诉求方面的作用不容忽视。本案例描述了北新建材的ESG实践过程与成果，旨在使学生充分了解ESG基本知识点，探究绿色债券如何赋能ESG，分析ESG如何助力企业创造价值，最后思考建材行业ESG现存问题的成因，总结北新ESG实践的经验，达到通过北新建材ESG实践为建材行业ESG实践提供参考的目的。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The proposal of “3060” shows that China attaches great importance to low-carbon development, and the energy consumption and carbon emissions of building materials industry chain account for more than half of the whole society. Reducing carbon in building materials industry is of great significance for implementing the “double-carbon” strategy. At the same time, residents pay more attention to health in the post-epidemic era, but problems such as string houses and high-pollution building materials have seriously damaged health, and whether the products of building materials enterprises are green or environmentally friendly has attracted much attention. As the largest new building materials industry group in China, Beixin&#39;s ESG practice plays an important role in promoting carbon reduction in building materials industry and responding to consumer demands. This case describes the ESG practice process and achievements of Beixin, aiming at enabling students to fully understand the basic knowledge of ESG, exploring how green bonds can empower ESG, analyzing how ESG can help enterprises create value, and finally thinking about the causes of the existing problems of ESG in building materials industry, summarizing the experience of Beixin, so as to provide reference for ESG practice in building materials industry through Beixin ESG practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG;绿色债券；信息不对称理论；企业社会责任理论；信号传递理论；共享价值创造理论；新质生产力；同群效应</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
